<% provide(:title, "LinGoChanって何") %>


<div class = "about_container row">

  <div class = "about_body col-md-12">

    <h1 class = "about_title">LinGoChanって何？</h1>

    <p>LinGoChanとは3種類の投稿を使って日本語を学べるサイトです</p>

    <div class = "about_head">

      <h2 class = "about_quasititle">3つの投稿手段で日本語を学ぼう！</h2>

      <div class = "about_statements">
        <p class = about_statement>1, お題</p>

        <p class = about_statement>2, ひとこと</p>

        <p class = about_statement>3, フィードバック</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class = "about_subject_post about_each_post">

      <p  class = "about_quasiquasititle">1, 「お題」を投稿しよう！</p>
      <%= image_tag (asset_path "subject_post.png", alt: "LimGoChan-subject_post", class: 'about_size') %>

    </div>


    <div class = "about_reply_post about_each_post">
      <p  class = "about_quasiquasititle">1, お題にたいして「ひとこと」を書こう！</p>
      <%= image_tag(asset_path "reply_post.png", alt: "LimGoChan-reply_post", class: 'about_size')%>
    </div>

    <div class = "about_feedback_post about_each_post">
      <p  class = "about_quasiquasititle">3, 「ひとこと」にたいして「フィードバック」をしよう！</p>
      <%= image_tag(asset_path "feedback_post.png", alt: "LimGoChan-feedback_post", class: 'about_size')%>
    </div>

      <p  class = "about_quasiquasititle">「フィードバック」は編集したり、削除したりできます</p>
    <div class = "about_subject_post">
      <%= image_tag(asset_path "edit_delete.png", alt: "LimGoChan-edit_delete", class: 'about_size')%>
    </div>

  </div>

</div>
